data.title: perfection!
data.text: He really knows hot to make great coffee! If your not sure what to order he recommend the perfect drink for you. So much better than starbucks!

data.title: What a nice place
data.text: Coffee places are always fast fast fast and no care factor, not this place.  While on a walk we stopped in to refill us and our dog and this was the nicest place with a great charm and i feel i have a new spot to get my drink as i head out of town or am out for a walk.  it reminds me of growing up with owners that still worked behind the counter.
